  "instructions": [
    "Heat olive oil in a large pot over medium heat.",
    "Add diced onion and cook until translucent, about 3 minutes.",
    "Stir in minced garlic and five‑spice powder, cooking for 1 minute until fragrant.",
    "Add diced carrots, celery, and potatoes; sauté for 5 minutes, stirring occasionally.",
    "Pour in vegetable stock and bring to a simmer.",
    "Stir in uncooked rice, reduce heat to low, cover, and simmer for 18 minutes until rice is tender.",
    "Add chopped kale and lemon juice, cooking until kale wilts, about 4 minutes.",
    "Season with salt and pepper, garnish with parsley, and serve hot."
